">Gianguido Mussomeli</a></span> </span> <span class="meta-tags" title="Tags"> <i class="icon-tags"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/adam-palka/" rel="tag">Adam Palka</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/ana-durlovski/" rel="tag">Ana Durlovski</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/diana-haller/" rel="tag">Diana Haller</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/edgardo-rocha/" rel="tag">edgardo rocha</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/gezym-myshketa/" rel="tag">Gezym Myshketa</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giuliano-carella/" rel="tag">Giuliano Carella</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/heinz-gohrig/" rel="tag">Heinz Ghrig</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/i-puritani/" rel="tag">I Puritani</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/jossi-wieler/" rel="tag">Jossi Wieler</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/roland-bracht/" rel="tag">Roland Bracht</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/sergio-morabito/" rel="tag">Sergio Morabito</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/staatsoper-stuttgart/" rel="tag">Staatsoper Stuttgart</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/staatsorchester-stuttgart/" rel="tag">Staatsorchester Stuttgart</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/vincenzo-bellini/" rel="tag">Vincenzo Bellini</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Adam Palka, Ana Durlovski, Diana Haller, edgardo rocha, Gezym Myshketa, Giuliano Carella, Heinz Ghrig, I Puritani, Jossi Wieler, Opera lirica, Roland Bracht, Sergio Morabito, Staatsoper Stuttgart, Staatsorchester Stuttgart, Vincenzo Bellini"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/e15610f34674f02caf174515ea5136d4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008